'''Nishikoyama Kofun''' (にしこやまこふん) is a mid-{{ill|Kofun period|ja|古墳時代}} burial mound located in Tannowa, Misaki Town, Sennan District, Osaka Prefecture. It is part of the {{ill|Tannowa Kofun Cluster|ja|淡輪古墳群}}, which also includes the {{ill|Nishiryo Kofun|ja|西陵古墳}}.
